<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> viracoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="21">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num> Āvatu koḻumattu Āḷuṭaiyār viracoḻa Ī<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>muṭaiyāṟku vaiykāvināṭṭu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>ya viranārāyaṇa<hi rend="grantha">śca</hi>tu<hi rend="grantha">rvvedi</hi> maṅkala <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>yaṇa mannaṟaiyiliṟ ceraṉai meṉkoṇṭacoḻaṉ peruvatikkuk kiḻakkun tiruvaraṅkavāykkālukku vaṭakku mutaṟ kaṇṇāṟṟu Añcāñcaturaṟattuṇṭattu meṟkaṭaiya nilame
<lb n="3"/>Araimāvum Ivvatikku meṟku Ivvāykkālukku vaṭakku Iraṇṭāyiraṅ kaṇṇāṟṟu Iraṇṭāñ catir ṉilanāl naṭuvil <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nilamiraṇṭu māviṟ kiḻkaṭaiya nila <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

